      "comment": "SHOWMAN BAZ (4) produced a fast 22.40 winning over 400m at this track last start in a Grade 5. In form and can measure up again. SPARKLING WHEELS (1) started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a strong early split, giving a sight but fading only late to finish second (29.81) at Wentworth Park over 520m. Well-placed to take this out. VINTAGE GLOW (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (22.78) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. LIGHTNING LOTTE (7) collected a minor prize last start over this track and distance - must be considered.",
